author: Life of Boris
description:
How much can you live on in 2025? 💸
I tried surviving 7 days on only €10 — no sponsors, no cheating, just Slav survival instincts and pure potato power.

In this Life of Boris budget challenge, I test if it’s still possible to live cheap in 2025 — with just €10 and maximum Slavic skill.
From shopping at Lidl to cooking legendary €1 meals, I’ll show you how to survive the week, stay full, and still have money left for garlic.

Featuring real cooking, financial wisdom, and mild suffering.
This is part 1 of the Slav on a Budget series — next up: “Living on €5 in One Day!”

If you like cheap cooking, funny survival challenges, and life advice from a man who once paid rent in potatoes, this video is for you.
